{"tid":221852,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(絲打入)period10日未完，食咩可以補下？","createTime":"2017-04-29T04:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T06:52:29.000Z","uid":91318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48bca91cdce6f02c997fd573a0ad7eb743904612","tid":221852,"uid":91318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:55:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n應該因爲2、3月時壓力太大<br />\n2月period完左之後到4月20先黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但一黎就黎左10日重未完<br />\n呢兩日feel到有啲暈 <br />\n唔知係咪黎太耐 失血過多搞到貧血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想知各位絲打有冇類似情況<br />\n同埋period緊食咩可以補下血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37abb26ebc29b616273d51aa8a3b839cfbc46843","tid":221852,"uid":52227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"黎緊補血你想死咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea762e3b079d7d58cb522c74cf1cc0a4fe9ddd4f","tid":221852,"uid":18370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:58:26.000Z","msg":"我果時食 norcolut 止血 <br />\n你血量好多？"},{"pid":"dc21e6dacca749e546a09142168cdd0147e12a3c","tid":221852,"uid":91318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T05:01:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊補血你想死咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前都好正常未試過咁樣<br />\n又final緊個人好冇精神溫書，想快啲搞搞佢<br />\n但真係唔知黎緊唔補得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1519123b3facc86349d6b37aa663393ac4d75883","tid":221852,"uid":91318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T05:02:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我果時食 norcolut 止血 <br />\n你血量好多？</blockquote><br />\n個人認為中等血量，但每次小便成個廁所都會紅曬，好似沖左杯cocktail咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f1d94d93ba61135c165ea123b5cef031332472","tid":221852,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T05:07:28.000Z","msg":"去睇下醫生好<br />\nd 女人就係有種無所謂既感覺<br />\n就放任自己"},{"pid":"8119f0cc469e4a8f5bef12a05b42c329cb110c1c","tid":221852,"uid":52227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T05:09:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黎緊補血你想死咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前都好正常未試過咁樣<br />\n又final緊個人好冇精神溫書，想快啲搞搞佢<br />\n但真係唔知黎緊唔補得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黎緊補血會黎得重多，你而家唔識停你點補都留唔到。<br />\n好似樓上咁止左血先好開始補。<br />\n你如果有多餘錢嘅就睇中醫，無嘅就ggl下有咩補血。<br />\n利申 我之前都好似你咁一黎就兩三個月，最長半年無停過成日係條街暈低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，睇左中醫半年唔夠得返4日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bec164b9d2921a239b6f9b816e855d00d84738e","tid":221852,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T05:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我果時食 norcolut 止血 <br />\n你血量好多？</blockquote><br />\n我2月果時又係 黎左10日 之後有埋尿炎<br />\n去睇醫生 食呢個就停左<br />\n但之後3至4月每月黎2次 量極少<br />\n5月冇黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12263edc8bedbf5826031efaed0b302392070395","tid":221852,"uid":91318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T05:17:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我果時食 norcolut 止血 <br />\n你血量好多？</blockquote><br />\n我2月果時又係 黎左10日 之後有埋尿炎<br />\n去睇醫生 食呢個就停左<br />\n但之後3至4月每月黎2次 量極少<br />\n5月冇黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGoogle左一下哩個係延經藥黎<br />\n啲人去旅行時會食，但之後會影響經期搞到亂曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9770e2f041493e15aca891970cdcf4445cfc843e","tid":221852,"uid":91318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T05:20:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>黎緊補血你想死咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前都好正常未試過咁樣<br />\n又final緊個人好冇精神溫書，想快啲搞搞佢<br />\n但真係唔知黎緊唔補得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黎緊補血會黎得重多，你而家唔識停你點補都留唔到。<br />\n好似樓上咁止左血先好開始補。<br />\n你如果有多餘錢嘅就睇中醫，無嘅就ggl下有咩補血。<br />\n利申 我之前都好似你咁一黎就兩三個月，最長半年無停過成日係條街暈低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，睇左中醫半年唔夠得返4日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黎三個月真係好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n戈時中醫有冇話你咩事？<br />\n<br />\nBtw有時覺得啲中醫好流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求其把個脈望兩望就執兩劑藥叫你扯"},{"pid":"842b85e92bb067cc895a8b7f292be90ef921fcb8","tid":221852,"uid":52227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T05:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黎緊補血會黎得重多，你而家唔識停你點補都留唔到。<br />\n好似樓上咁止左血先好開始補。<br />\n你如果有多餘錢嘅就睇中醫，無嘅就ggl下有咩補血。<br />\n利申 我之前都好似你咁一黎就兩三個月，最長半年無停過成日係條街暈低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，睇左中醫半年唔夠得返4日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n黎三個月真係好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n戈時中醫有冇話你咩事？<br />\n<br />\nBtw有時覺得啲中醫好流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求其把個脈望兩望就執兩劑藥叫你扯[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n中醫真係唔好睇平，好多都好廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話我氣虛血虛所以個身留唔住啲血。<br />\n我開頭都唔信，比人迫左去睇又睇得好:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw 戒口好緊要，我有時唔戒凍飲又食多左甜野佢把左陣都把得出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f1cfbacf8c9bbe2f74b4a45315cc8c9bf4eba5","tid":221852,"uid":91318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T06:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中醫真係唔好睇平，好多都好廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話我氣虛血虛所以個身留唔住啲血。<br />\n我開頭都唔信，比人迫左去睇又睇得好:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw 戒口好緊要，我有時唔戒凍飲又食多左甜野佢把左陣都把得出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但咁樣睇半年都好金下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ab44c1b8d3bbefaf664cac1dbd2f17c3925ce5","tid":221852,"uid":52227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T06:49:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中醫真係唔好睇平，好多都好廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話我氣虛血虛所以個身留唔住啲血。<br />\n我開頭都唔信，比人迫左去睇又睇得好:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw 戒口好緊要，我有時唔戒凍飲又食多左甜野佢把左陣都把得出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但咁樣睇半年都好金下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇一次500蚊連5日藥，之後自己出藥房執通常可以平1/3左右，一星期藥你預250-350左右，每一個月覆一次診<br />\n<br />\n<del>咁計落半年都未夠一萬嘅</del> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d08338a30e55eaa555ba7f67b43c2ec93e6476","tid":221852,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T06:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我果時食 norcolut 止血 <br />\n你血量好多？</blockquote><br />\n我2月果時又係 黎左10日 之後有埋尿炎<br />\n去睇醫生 食呢個就停左<br />\n但之後3至4月每月黎2次 量極少<br />\n5月冇黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGoogle左一下哩個係延經藥黎<br />\n啲人去旅行時會食，但之後會影響經期搞到亂曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一向都亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}